Jewel Cave National Monument.title: Jewel Cave National Monument
Jewel Cave National Monument.byline: Jewel Cave National Monument is in the Black Hills of South Dakota.

Jewish Autonomous Oblast.title: Jewish Autonomous Oblast
Jewish Autonomous Oblast.byline: Russia's Jewish Autonomous Oblast (Russian: Евре́йская автоно́мная о́бласть, eev-RAY-skuh-yuh ahf-tah-NOHM-nuh-yuh OH-blust') is a region in the Russian Far East, which borders Amur Oblast to the west, Khabarovsk Krai to the north, and China to the south.
